column1: horough mode, identifies PuTTY private key (.ppk), Remote Desktop Connection (.rdp), and RSA token (.sdtid) files, and extracts private key and session information.
ject -Class 'CIM_DataFile' -Filter "Drive='C:' AND extension='ppk' OR extension='rdp' OR extension='.sdtid'" -ComputerName $RemoteComputer @optionalCreds | Select Name)
